Fixed the post, put and delete requests

Created Users and the ability to add and delete users
Merged mongodb branch into master as finished working with mongo
Added Password and email checking for users to allow them to login
For the user sign up method I added a jwt token once the login is successful
Added Authentication to all the post put and delete methods
Added a new find by name get
Fixed some issues with the get methods
